data.description: A hidden gem nestled in the heart of Lacey, Southlake is where nature & convenience seamlessly coexist. Peacefully situated between the inviting shores of Long Lake & Hicks Lake, offering quick public access to waterfront tranquility & wooded walking trails, while keeping essential amenities mere minutes away.This immaculate home features a downstairs office/den, a formal dining room, & bright, open concept, great room. Upstairs, you’ll find a spacious bonus room & 4 generous bedrooms. The primary bedroom offers serene views of the protected green space & private backyard, while offering a luxurious ensuite 5-piece bathroom. You'll love the 3-car tandem garage w/ built-ins for added storage. Just 25 mins to JBLM makes commuting a breeze.
